  <CalDefinition Description="The CSM and Low radio shall provide two additional boost calibrations to allow the development engineer to set the final headroom for the Front and Rear channels once values for all parametric EQ have been finalized.  This setting ensures that the system can reach its maximum loudness specification.  There is one setting for the Front channels and a second for the Rear." Name="VSE_PARAM_EQ_R_HR" References="GIS-604-440" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU">
